2. Pull the dino to that spot. <br>
3. Engage pet. <br>
4. Take off to the other end with your pet targeted. <br>
5. Med up until the pet's health bar disappears. <br>
6. Stand up and cast another pet and DS it. <br>
7. Sit and wait. <br>
8. When the Dino get there, repeat from step 3.<br>
<br>
NOTE: Keep track of the Dino's health. If it is low, don't wander too far. If you are too far away when it dies, you get NO experience.<br>
<br>
Tips: <br>
Use the level 51 earth pet instead of the 57 for mana conservation<br>
Use shield of lava instead of cadeau of flame for mana conservation<br>
<br>
I did this but found it to be a complete waste of time. After one kill taking 10 minutes, I gated and went somewhere else. <p><img src=http://www.garlic.com/~hypatia/images/staff.gif width=405 height=36><br>
