<br>
Sic fully buffed pet on him stand fair ways off, 2 hits from BWS, the get  some distance off.<br>
<br>
pet dies, cast new one, send him in, use buff from leggings. Two hits form staff..run away.<br>
Rinse, repeat 4-7 pets does him for cost of 3-4 bubbs.<br>
